Yes — the structure looks right for Phase 4B:

COPY content/profiles/ /profiles/

That is the correct path as long as your Phase 4A Python default is:

profile_root=Path(getenv("PXE_PROFILE_ROOT", "/profiles")),

But Phase 4B is only complete if each YAML file has valid contents. From the screenshot, 10-developer-workstation.yml looks empty right now, so do not transfer/build yet unless you already added the content after the picture.

